Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:19.28,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,本機預定將於十分鐘後在那霸機場著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:23.00,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,現在時間是上午10時40分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:26.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,天氣晴 氣溫28.9℃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:36.07,haruka-title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(415.334,900.001)}{\fs70\}{\blur1\i1}{\fad(420,370)}並不需要什麼王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:32.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:33.77,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我來啦 沖繩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.48,haruka-screen,,0,0,0,,{\frz6.355\pos(933.334,363.332)}{\fs55}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.48,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}PS:廣告板上的是沖繩方言。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,南國的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.12,haruka-screen2,,0,0,0,,{\frz338.3\move(703.199,431.6,701.8,383.466)}{\move(903.999,758,0,0)}古宇利島\N駕車游
