Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.11,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我想去古宇利大橋看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.28,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,看起來好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,過了橋就是沙灘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:54.77,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.36,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那個女生 個頭好大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.08,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,真的哦 是模特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.59,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,遙到了沖繩之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:14.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,立刻打電話給我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉只能讓你一個人出國工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,畢竟我不會英語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.03,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不要給別人添麻煩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.60,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,對了 你的表妹彼方也在奶奶家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,還記得她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:36.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.47,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:48.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦 難道是和媽媽走散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:52.35,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那個 你是大空遙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我是比嘉彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你是彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我們最後一次見面是在四年級時的暑假對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你看 這張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.62,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那時我和你差不多一樣高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.40,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我以為現在應該也一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:30.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,對了 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:34.01,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,聽說我要和彼方住同一個房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你地方變窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但今後也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.32,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我房間還蠻大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.67,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這種距離感怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,明明今後還要住在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好擔心將來的生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.30,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.98,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沒有海邊的腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.99,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,而且完全沒有一絲海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼 好神奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 怎麼回事 好厲害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.80,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有海浪呢 好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.21,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,泳衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,水是透明的 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.01,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.67,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,游泳 衝浪 潛水都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.92,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,家的附近就有這樣的海灘 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:48.90,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:51.87,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,龜吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,咦 小遙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:57.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,在海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.85,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,啊呀啊呀 這麼著急嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.66,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我有點擔心她 所以換身衣服後就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.99,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,也是 去玩得開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.64,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,成美曾經練習的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好像至今還有人使用一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:37.90,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.56,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.54,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,忘記防曬 忘記防曬了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,本來一到這裡就該塗防曬霜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.16,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,喂 那邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.11,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,上面 球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:16.88,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.40,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:19.73,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:22.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:25.15,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙灘排球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我可以看一看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.92,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好強的壓迫力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:49.13,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:56.23,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.23,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.46,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這樣打可以打得更高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.41,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,在沙灘排球裡上手托球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,更容易被判犯規哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.77,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.21,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以吧 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:25.62,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,彩紗說可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:26.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:31.35,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,初次見面 我叫大空遙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:32.86,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,是高二生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:35.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我們是同齡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.47,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我叫立花彩紗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:41.50,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,她是和我一起組隊的 遠井成美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:42.67,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,請多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:52.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我今天才剛搬來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.72,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,以後要住在表妹的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你們兩位是沖繩本地人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.47,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不 我來自京都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不過成美很久之前就住在這裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:03.91,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.00,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.91,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你來發球可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我托球給你之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:13.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,按剛才教你的方法試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,知道了 我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.45,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,跳得好高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.75,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,本來還以為能打得更遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,腳陷在沙子裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,作為第一次來說 球線飛得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:43.90,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:48.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,說不定未來的王牌就在現在誕生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:50.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,說的有點過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.37,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.36,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.22,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,麻煩你不要把王牌這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這麼輕易地掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.53,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,等等 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙灘排球是兩個人的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.41,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙灘排球裡不需要什麼「王牌」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.77,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我是不是說了什麼不該說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好啦 她今天第一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.60,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,算了 明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:40.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你們兩人認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這個場地非常乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.62,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,就好像至今還有人使用一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:08.61,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那為什麼你在那個時候沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:28.24,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:34.16,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要不要打一場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,七分制比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.58,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,只要大空這邊得到一分就算你們贏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:41.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.86,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣 我想打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.45,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,等等 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以吧 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.27,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,哪邊開球都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.27,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎 那讓我們來發球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.27,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好 我燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:15.14,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那個 難道說規則之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.34,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我很擅長運動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.46,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,排球也在體育課上打過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.85,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大概差不多的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.26,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.80,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.90,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.19,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,剛剛是因為風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:40.15,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,現在剛好是海風吹得最猛的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我沒有考慮風的因素呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:47.29,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不過也有反過來利用風的技術哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沙灘排球受風的影響很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.56,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以每七分就要交換一次場地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.44,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.56,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你有打過沙灘排球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.49,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,以前打過一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.59,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但你懂得好多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.48,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,而且彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.73,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你終於肯看著我和我說話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.41,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,因為要打比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以不得不向你做最低程度的說明而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.60,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,即便如此我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,差不多可以開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:35.32,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.07,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,正中央的高球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.92,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話我也能夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.91,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.15,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不小心發出了奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.89,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,對不起 讓你臉著地了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.03,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:20.20,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,接下來我會注意前後左右的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.20,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,她較真了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.59,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,現在到賽點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,軌跡和最初那球一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:09.43,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.59,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話就不會刺到眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.07,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,打到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.41,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,彼方 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:34.24,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,成美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.52,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,屁股摔成兩瓣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,一開始就是兩瓣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我們輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:29.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這下你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.98,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,必須要兩個人才能把球打回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.03,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不管少了其中哪一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,都無法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,只有兩人並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我們才能立於球場之上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:45.65,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以 沙灘排球不需要王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.30,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,雖然今天我的實力還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.26,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但既然如此 我會多多練習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.80,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,因為很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:11.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要是練熟了的話 一定會更好玩對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,成美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:27.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我要復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:30.08,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我們再來一局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:35.45,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,等等小遙 不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:37.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.50,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:40.88,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.03,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎 成美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.22,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但是我有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:48.94,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不是現在比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:49.75,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:51.92,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,一週之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:55.98,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,如果那時你能把規則記住 認真進行基礎訓練的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:58.47,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,再和你打一次也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我明白了 我會認真練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.53,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,等等小遙 這兩個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.79,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,規則的話彼方也會好好教給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.68,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:09.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那我們約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.72,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好 我要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我的鬥志在熊熊燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.23,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,下次一定要打敗你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,要練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}要做基礎訓練了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.12,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.13,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那兩個人原來是高中生冠軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:50.70,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 她們是京都強校的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.75,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼不告訴我呀 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.17,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我本打算告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但感覺你沒打算聽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.16,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.49,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,但要是知道了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:05.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你就不會夸下復仇的海口了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.13,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不 就算知道也還是會試著去挑戰她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:09.68,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,那不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:13.15,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 一分總能拿到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.97,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我對自己的運動神經還蠻有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:19.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好 明天開始要特訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:19.96,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.96,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你哼什麼呢 彼方也要一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.23,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,反正是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.44,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你剛才怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:35.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,你問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.93,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,感覺你剛才對初學者發了好大的脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.38,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:42.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,而且連復仇戰都接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,只要打上一週她就能明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.17,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,明白什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:47.54,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:52.51,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,比如讓比嘉同學藉這個機會回來什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:58.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,和這件事沒有關係 對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:11.69,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,明明說了今天是小遙的歡迎會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:15.49,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,爺爺卻去參加什麼町內會的聚會了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.42,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,竟然做了這麼多菜來招待我 太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.01,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:23.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這些全都是沖繩料理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 都是奶奶親手做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.02,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這個是豆腐炒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.43,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我媽媽最喜歡吃這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:32.12,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:36.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不愧是姐妹 連喜好都一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:39.29,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,以前也很喜歡這個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:41.57,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.05,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沖繩豬肉味噌湯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.99,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,沖繩的節日料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.10,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,今天做了不少運動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.14,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,感覺能比平時多吃一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 沙灘排球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:06.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 真的很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:08.25,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我還打得很爛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:09.68,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:10.88,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我說奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:11.35,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.82,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,彼方以前打過沙灘排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.60,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,現在不打了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.24,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:22.74,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,現在暫時…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:37.09,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,所以小遙能到這邊來 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.63,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,一定要和那孩子好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:51.85,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,收拾行李就慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:53.21,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:54.08,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:56.16,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,好像有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:00.33,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,烏龜？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:01.67,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,它是龜吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.26,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不會咬人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:05.95,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:08.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,它是個乖巧的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,對吧 龜吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:15.06,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,我也能摸摸它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:16.29,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:18.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,龜吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:20.24,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.31,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.87,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,難道我被嫌棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:35.71,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,不好說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:37.39,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:39.19,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,明明我們今天才見面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.37,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}龜吉 讓我看看嘛 讓我摸摸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.18,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}龜吉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:44.55,haruka-text,,0,0,0,,大空遙 沖繩生活從今天開始了
